####authorization code mode

### get code
# chrome input
# http://127.0.0.1:8178/oauth/authorize?client_id=shenyu&redirect_uri=https://dromara.org/zh/projects/soul/overview/&response_type=code&scope=read_userinfo
# if need login, account is testUser, password is password
# then OAuth Approval
# then you will get a code with callback in uri

### get token
# !!!Pay attention to replace the code value!!!
# Please write down access_token and refresh_token value from response
POST http://localhost:8178/oauth/token
Authorization: Basic shenyu password
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=authorization_code&redirect_uri=https://dromara.org/zh/projects/soul/overview/&code=QDvGp0

